title: [Bloodriven Village, Bailey Park]
description: An uneven stone wall serves as the village's southernmost border.  Frost-laden conifers rise above it, their lowest branches brushing over the mortar dust along the wall's top edge.  A carved wooden dog sits at the corner as the road turns to the north.
